invalid type: string "---\n\n## 3. How are the placements at C-DAC?\n\n**Answer:**\n\nC-DAC provides active campus placement assistance.\n\n### Placement Highlights\n\n- More than **400 companies** participate in the pan-India placement drives.\n- Typical salary packages range from **‚āĻ5‚Äď6 LPA** to **‚āĻ13 LPA**.\n- The final package depends on:\n  - C-DAC center\n  - Academic background\n\nˇˇˇ